(65, 1, '2022-08-19 12:00:50', '2022-08-19 12:00:50', 'Cardiac emergencies are life threatening. They can arise due to various causes. Whatever may be the cause, the resulting damage is devastating. So the eponym “When the bolt strikes…” is indeed very appropriate to describe cardiac emergencies.\r\n<h3 class="sub-ttl">Acute Heart Attack Definition</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">“<a href="https://healthlibrary.askapollo.com/how-to-prevent-heart-attack/">Heart Attack</a>“, technically termed Myocardial Infarction, is a result of total blockage of the blood vessel (coronary artery) which supplies blood to the heart. The blockage is due to the formation of plug composed of cholesterol, blood cells, fibrin and calcium.</p>', 'Health and Lifestyle', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'health-and-lifestyle', '', '', '2022-08-22 09:37:24', '2022-08-22 09:37:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hospital/?page_id=65', 0, 'page', '', 0),
